 { q: 'Do small businesses need company shirts?', a: 'Any business where employees interact with customers, vendors, or the public benefits from branded apparel. Trades and field service especially — a uniformed tech closes more jobs than a guy in a random t-shirt. Even 2–3 person crews see a meaningful trust lift from consistent branded shirts.' },
